WEBVTT

00:00:29.974 --> 00:00:31.778
in the Amazon Rainforest

00:00:31.778 --> 00:00:33.618
is not the jaguar,

00:00:33.618 --> 00:00:35.343
it's not the harpy eagle,

00:00:35.343 --> 00:00:39.164
it's the isolated and uncontacted tribes.

00:00:39.164 --> 00:00:42.613
Now four years ago, I injured my 
foot in a climbing accident

00:00:42.613 --> 00:00:44.147
and I went to the doctor.

00:00:44.147 --> 00:00:45.741
She gave me heat,

00:00:45.741 --> 00:00:48.445
she gave me cold, aspirin,

00:00:48.445 --> 00:00:51.675
narcotic painkillers, anti-inflammatories,

00:00:51.675 --> 00:00:53.542
cortisone shots.

00:00:53.542 --> 00:00:55.559
It didn't work.

00:00:55.559 --> 00:00:57.396
Several months later,

00:00:57.396 --> 00:00:59.613
I was in the northeast Amazon,

